>> time required: 12 hours
>> course: side

Put pan on high heat and add @garlic cloves{5} until charred
Add peel of @lemon{0.5} and @bay leaves{2} until lightly charred
Add @chili flakes{1%tbsp} until well toasted
Remove from heat add @olive oil{125%ml}, @smoked paprika{1%tsp}, and @salt{0.5%tsp}
Add @feta{180%g} to oil and leave out to marinate.
Can be stored in fridge.
